These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, chef, firefighter
1. the chef is on the far left##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | chef | firefighter | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, bartender, writer
1. the writer is on the far right##1
2. the designer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | designer | bartender | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | photography | magic-tricks | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
