.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, scientific, adventure
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | comedy | scientific |

